    <p>My name is Mirka and I am distant PhD student in Intelligent Systems study program at Technical University of Kosice, Slovakia. My thesis is about Methods of symbolic artificial intelligence in social robotics. My goal is to make a creative program. Currently, I am working on a system that writes haiku poetry.</p>
