    <p>If you have any comments or suggestions, please do not hesitate to write me an email: miroslava.hreskova(at)student.tuke.sk</p>
    <p>Or you can share your ideas with me through a questionnaire <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1i5bKrlbJONJGfWWndMhmVOUVlttd2sXVfLdMkKjBAs0">HERE</a></p>
